{"tid":1277217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"震撼人心  警方攻堅前 「香港小妹妹」搶救立法會4死士","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:43:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4ab34ac29b880af44e837e1b01fe10f0acc4e6","tid":1277217,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpwgmFsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpwgmFsE.jpg&h=42c4bd18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n香港民眾昨（1日）上街展開七一反送中大遊行，更有示威者衝進立法會大樓占領議場，最後在警方強勢驅離下只得撤退，而也是在這個時候出現了震撼人心的一幕，那就是4名死士死守立法會時，傳有個小妹妹毅然決然地走了進去，準備將這4人救出。<br />\n<br />\n經常分享中國與兩岸狀況的「說中國」臉書粉專透露，有港人在網路上留言指出，當時香港小妹妹沒有猶豫也沒有什麼悲壯的神情，走向議場內試圖救人。<br />\n<br />\n當時有人詢問她「警方要攻堅了，妳不怕被困在裡面？」小妹妹則霸氣地回了一句「要留，一起留。要走，一起走。」這樣的場景讓不少港人震驚，直呼沒想到連小妹妹也變得如此勇敢。<br />\n<br />\n一名當時在現場的香港記者在網路上表示，警方半夜0時攻堅死線要到時，十多名年輕人衝進議場把死士帶走，其中就有好幾名年輕女孩，記者問她們害不害怕時，女孩們直說「4個義士一定要救」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpw3DR7F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpw3DR7F.jpg&h=a3dc1943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2840125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2840125&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME%2F56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=43d7e621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2840125&h=bf4de999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2840125</a>"},{"pid":"8da0d81bae84b6c26b3c0b115357e92b4719e179","tid":1277217,"uid":23098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"比催淚彈更催淚"}]}